<plot>A business dinner turns romantic when Lisa and Jason meet. Jason seizes the opportunity and asks her out on a date. When she reveals she is trans-gender, Jason has to figure out if he's really ready to take a chance on love. This story, both universal and specific to the trans-gender experience, will delight genre aficionados and is also suitable for a crossover audience.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?064175</url></doc>
